        {
            "title": "台積電首季純利按年增長58.3% 晶圓先進製程出貨佔比達74%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台積電公布今年首季業績，稅後純利達5724.8億元(新台幣‧下同)，按年升58.3%，按季也提升13.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：台積電官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內營業收入淨額逾1.13萬元，較去年同期的8392.54億元增長35.1%，較去年第4季的逾1.04萬億元也高8.4%。毛利率66.2%，營業利益率58.1%，稅後純利率50.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若以美元計，首季營收359億美元，按年升40.6%，按季增長6.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內晶圓銷售額當中，約25%來自3奈米製程出貨，5奈米製程出貨則佔36%，7奈米製程出貨佔13%。總體而言，先進製程(包含7奈米及更先進製程)的營收，達到全季晶圓銷售金額的74%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15880180-%e5%8f%b0%e7%a9%8d%e9%9b%bb%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b758-3-%e6%99%b6%e5%9c%93%e5%85%88%e9%80%b2%e8%a3%bd%e7%a8%8b%e5%87%ba%e8%b2%a8%e4%bd%94%e6%af%94",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241017_FI_source-web_tsmc-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 13:54:51",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
