        {
            "title": "半日收市︱動力加強 恒指升359點報26306點 科股領漲 寧德時代破頂",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">外圍持續向好，日股今早創新高，加上內地首季經濟增長勝預期，港股今早重新收復兩萬六，科股是升市火車頭，寧德時代(03750)則成藍籌最強。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開175點、報26122點即成半日低位，早市前半段尚只在26122點至26220點之間橫行，於上午10時半左右動力開始加強，步入拾級向上階段，最高曾見26320點，升372點後於高位整固。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"藍思科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/06613-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"藍思科技官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/06613-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">藍思科技官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"藍思科技官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/06613-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">藍思科技官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指中午收報26306點，漲359點或1.38%。恒生科技指數明顯跑贏，半日升146點或2.98%，報5058點；國企指數升151點或1.73%，報8869點。主板半日成交1297.76億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指半日升335點，報26316點，高水9點。科指期貨升138點，報5063點，高水5點。國指期貨升150點，報8873點，高水4點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅科股是升市主要功臣，獲花旗選為網絡AI領域首選的阿里巴巴(09988)與騰訊(00700)，齊躋身藍籌升幅10大榜，亦是對恒指貢獻最多點數升幅的兩隻股份。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴剛發布可用於遊戲開發的AI模型Happy Oyster，這款新工具可創建三維互動視頻，可用於製作電影、電視劇及遊戲；該股半日升4.59%，報134.5元。騰訊也漲2.81%，報513元，上述兩股分別為恒指帶來90點及逾56點進賬。「ATM」最後1位成員美團(03690)今早也升2.55%，報88.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藍籌升幅10大榜上的重磅科股，尚有百度(09888)與網易(09999)，其中百度是表現次佳恒指成分股，半日升8.38%，報124.1元；網易則升4.62%，報185.9元。單計「ATM」、百度及網易，5隻股份合共已令恒指升超過203點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">至於藍籌升幅榜首則穩入寧德時代囊中，該股經過去兩日受集資傳聞困擾逆市報跌，在昨晚派發首季勝預期的成績表後，今早股價報復式反彈，更破頂創上市以來新高，最高曾衝上724.5元，升10.53%，半日低位684.5元時也升4.42%；中午收報723元，漲67.5元或10.3%，半日成交達26.13億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">里昂搶先上調寧德時代目標價，由710元升至740元，指該公司首季業績在面對鋰價上升的環境下仍勝預期，相信該公司由今季起可以開始將成本轉嫁，推動毛利率改善。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">價量齊升的科股亦數不在少，近期熱炒的滴普科技(01384)半日飆19.43%，報75.6元，成交17.99億元。被視為「港股GPU第一股」的壁仞科技(06082)創新高，中午收報46.84元，漲21.41%，成交也有10.21億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，iPhone概念股藍思科技(06613)首季由盈轉虧，隨即遭券商降目標價；該股今早裂口低開7.68%後一直捱沽，最低曾見15.68元，挫20.24%，創歷史新低；中午收報16.88元，仍跌14.14%，半日成交7.82億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">花旗明言藍思科技上季業績遜預期，表現令人失望，但仍相信該公司有望受惠年中至第3季的iOS補貨情緒，維持對該股「買入」評級，目標價由27元降至25元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"藍思科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/06613-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"藍思科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/06613-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">藍思科技官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">里昂也承認藍思科技面對短期挑戰，但長期而言在可折疊手機、智能眼鏡及AI伺服器等領域仍有增長動力，維持「跑贏大市」評級，目標價則由31.5元降至24元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">至於發盈喜的中金公司(03908)與龍蟠科技(02465)，今早則應聲造好，龍蟠科技尤其突出，半日漲22.31%，報16.23元，創3個月新高；中金公司也升4.05%，報20.04元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，今日登場的新股思格新能(06656)亦未有令人失望，中午收報595元，較招股價324.2元高83.53%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15879843-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8b%95%e5%8a%9b%e5%8a%a0%e5%bc%b7-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87359%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126306%e9%bb%9e-%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98%e6%bc%b2-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7",
