        {
            "title": "A股半日升   深股創板升逾1%至2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日升，深股跑贏滬股，半日升近1.7%，創業板指數升2.66%，兩市成交合計 14618.69億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日報4048，升21點或0.53%，今早以4030點開市，升2點或0.07%，早段見4028點，升1點，三頭馬車數據公布，大市向上，尾段見4052，升25點或0.62%，為上午高位。半日成交6007.52億元</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日報14743，升244點或1.69%，今早開市報14546點，亦升47點或0.33%。早段見14522，跌24點或0.17%，為半日低位，後段高見14751點，升253點或1.75%，為半日高位，半日成交8611.17億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日升42點或0.9%，今早開升9點或0.2%，開報4694點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日升93點或2.66%，報3608點，今早開市報3531點，升16點或0.46%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國家統計局公布首季經濟增長5%，勝市場預期的4.8%。</p>\n</div>",
